                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A4/3: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Harvey</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-07-10T21:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 10, 1921—9 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 10—5:18 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>573. Your July 9, 7 p.m. Prime Minister says statement is admirable. He wholly
                    approves and I am giving out statement to newspapers here tonight for
                    publication tomorrow morning. I assume you are doing the same thing.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harvey</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
